			<tr>
				<td width="150" height="25" valign="top"><span class="sub">Categories:</span></td>
				<td>
					On the Edit Categories form you can create new and edit existing categories of the web site.<br><br>
					
					To rename a category, select the category and press the Rename button.<br><br>
					
					To delete all articles of a category select the category and press the Empty button.<br><br>
					
					To create a new Category, enter the Category name and press the Create button.
				</td>
			</tr>
		</table>
		
		<a name="art"></a>
		<table width="500">
			
			<tr height="5"><td colspan="2">&nbsp;</td></tr>
			
			<tr>
				<td width="150" height="25" valign="top"><span class="sub">Articles:</span></td>
				<td>
					On the Edit Articles form you can create new and edit existing articles of the web site.<br><br>
					
					To post a new article to the web site, press the Rename button.<br><br>
					
					To edit a particular article press the Edit button in the Action field.<br><br>
					
					To delete a particular article press the Del button in the Action field.<br><br>
					
					You can search for an article by using the search form, enter the search keyword and press the search button.<br><br>
					
					You can select how many articles to display by selecting the entries per page.<br><br>
					
					You can sort the articles by clicking on the appropriate field title.
				</td>
			</tr>
			
